  "description": "<p>If you exhibit some evidence of corruption, NPCs will most likely react to those pieces of evidence. However, sometimes the corruption within a character is hidden from view but somehow still noticed, intuited, or even subconsciously reacted to by NPCs. These reactions can be the most creepy because they appear to be an illogical and involuntary response in the NPCs.</p>",
